            ....:         n_non_simplex_faces += 1
            ....:     else:
            ....:         it.ignore_subfaces()
            ....:
            sage: n_non_simplex_faces
            127

        Face iterator must not be in dual mode::

            sage: it = C.face_generator(algorithm='dual')
            sage: _ = next(it)
            sage: it.ignore_subfaces()
            Traceback (most recent call last):
            ...
